photos.alt: A photo of two persons standing near a fence of a terrace, looking into the distance. One of them is gesticulating with her hand, as if pointing towards something. The pair is in focus, as well as the dark green painted and slightly dilapidated metal fence with swashes. The rest is out of focus, with an old building visible on the left, and a few trees visible on the right. The sky is overcast and is bright grey.
